com.gembox.spreadsheet.internal.inlinestyles

Class RichTextString

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gembox.spreadsheet.internal.inlinestyles.RichTextString
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.gembox.internal.core.Equatable<RichTextString>, Iterable<RichTextRun>

    public final class RichTextString
extends Object
implements com.gembox.internal.core.Equatable<RichTextString>, Iterable<RichTextRun>
    Some strings in the workbook may have formatting applied at a level that is more granular than the cell level. For instance, specific characters within the string may be bolded, have coloring, italicizing, etc. In these cases, the formatting is stored along with the text in instances of this class.
